(7, '<p style="text-align:center"><strong>Há»™i há»¯u nghá»‹ Viá»‡t Nam - Cá»™ng h&ograve;a S&eacute;c</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><strong>SpoleÄnost Vietnamsko-Äesk&eacute;ho pÅ™aÌtelstviÌ</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><strong>Viet Nam - Czech Republic Friendship Association</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><br />\r\nHá»™i há»¯u nghá»‹ Viá»‡t Nam - S&eacute;c th&agrave;nh láº­p ng&agrave;y 10/1/1997 theo quy&ecirc;Ìt Ä‘iÌ£nh s&ocirc;Ì 20/QÄ TTg cuÌ‰a ThuÌ‰ tÆ°Æ¡Ìng ChiÌnh phuÌ‰ sau khi coÌ quy&ecirc;Ìt Ä‘iÌ£nh cuÌ‰a ThÆ°Æ¡Ì€ng vuÌ£ B&ocirc;Ì£ ChiÌnh triÌ£ Ä‘&ocirc;Ì€ng yÌ cho giaÌ‰i th&ecirc;Ì‰ H&ocirc;Ì£i hÆ°Ìƒu nghiÌ£ Vi&ecirc;Ì£t Nam - Ti&ecirc;Ì£p KhÄƒÌc Ä‘&ecirc;Ì‰ thaÌ€nh l&acirc;Ì£p hai h&ocirc;Ì£i ri&ecirc;ng bi&ecirc;Ì£t laÌ€ H&ocirc;Ì£i hÆ°Ìƒu nghiÌ£ Vi&ecirc;Ì£t Nam - SeÌc vaÌ€ H&ocirc;Ì£i hÆ°Ìƒu nghiÌ£ Vi&ecirc;Ì£t Nam - Xl&ocirc;vakia. &Ocirc;ng Nguy&ecirc;Ìƒn Xu&acirc;n Chu&acirc;Ì‰n, ThÆ°Ì trÆ°Æ¡Ì‰ng B&ocirc;Ì£ C&ocirc;ng nghi&ecirc;Ì£p, laÌ€m ChuÌ‰ tiÌ£ch H&ocirc;Ì£i khoÌa I; &ocirc;ng Nguy&ecirc;Ìƒn Minh H&ocirc;Ì€ng, ThÆ°Ì trÆ°Æ¡Ì‰ng B&ocirc;Ì£ Th&ocirc;ng tin &amp; Truy&ecirc;Ì€n Th&ocirc;ng laÌ€m ChuÌ‰ tiÌ£ch H&ocirc;Ì£i khoÌa II vaÌ€ khoÌa III.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>I/ T&ocirc;n chá»‰, má»¥c Ä‘&iacute;ch:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">H&ocirc;Ì£i hÆ°Ìƒu nghiÌ£ Vi&ecirc;Ì£t nam - SeÌc laÌ€ m&ocirc;Ì£t t&ocirc;Ì‰ chÆ°Ìc chiÌnh triÌ£- xaÌƒ h&ocirc;Ì£i; laÌ€ m&ocirc;Ì£t trong 99 t&ocirc;Ì‰ chÆ°Ìc thaÌ€nh vi&ecirc;n cuÌ‰a Li&ecirc;n hi&ecirc;Ì£p caÌc t&ocirc;Ì‰ chÆ°Ìc hÆ°Ìƒu nghiÌ£ Vi&ecirc;Ì£t Nam; hoaÌ£t Ä‘&ocirc;Ì£ng theo Äi&ecirc;Ì€u l&ecirc;Ì£ H&ocirc;Ì£i, Äi&ecirc;Ì€u l&ecirc;Ì£ cuÌ‰a Li&ecirc;n hi&ecirc;Ì£p caÌc t&ocirc;Ì‰ chÆ°Ìc hÆ°Ìƒu nghiÌ£ Vi&ecirc;Ì£t Nam vaÌ€ tu&acirc;n thuÌ‰ lu&acirc;Ì£t phaÌp nÆ°Æ¡Ìc C&ocirc;Ì£ng hoÌ€a xaÌƒ h&ocirc;Ì£i chuÌ‰ nghiÌƒa Vi&ecirc;Ì£t Nam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:ju